name: Catshionist / Trader cat #1
description:
Catshohionist is a set of drawings that take my furry children as a model and transform them into celebrities wearing trendy dresses...
Trader cat is a drawing of my son Google, wearing a superb Armani outfit, after having succeeded in the world of trading.
It was made with the help of Adobe Fresco and exported to MP3 format with the Windows video editor.
